HEADWORD: medicaid
<hw>medicaid</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A program controlled by the United
States government to provide health care for the needy. It is funded by
contributions from the salaries of workers, and is therefore a form of
health insurance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Medical</ent>⟦br⟧
